An application to easily collect, save, manage and export citations in multiple formats, simply by entering PubMed IDs.

Reference Stacker is currently testing on Heroku

http://references.heroku.com/

Reference Stacker uses the BioRuby gem.

http://www.bioruby.org/

The Ruby on Rails tutorial by Michael Hartl is an excellent way to learn RoR.

http://www.railstutorial.org/
